  "projectName": "Masca Dashboard",
  "projectDescription": "A multi-vendor SaaS dashboard built with Vue 3 and Firebase that enables vendors to manage orders, sync products between Bsale POS and Shopify, process payments via MercadoPago, and coordinate deliveries through Uber Direct.",
